    ns1:numberOfCredits 3.0 ;
    ns1:otherInformation "The subject is clearly related to objective number 4 as the English language is the lingua franca of science and technology and the most used official language and the most widely spoken second language. English is a life-long learning skill that will also enable students to access millions of pages on the Internet and have knowledge from all the universities teaching in English at the click of a button."@es ;
