<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/595040064/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """In the progressive evaluation, still referred to as "continuous" in this guide, there are two tests for evaluating grammar, vocabulary, listening and writing, the weight of the tests is 40 % each. 10 % of the mark depends on class participation. There will be a presentation, recorded or face-to-face, to evaluate the speaking skill with a value of 10 %.
The Global exam includes the contents of both tests 1 and 2. It has a weight of 90 %. There will also be an audio recording for testing the speaking skill. with a weight of 10 %. .
The extraordinary exam will be equivalent to the global one."""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/595040064/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/595040064/2025-26/evaluation/trial2>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/595040064/2025-26/evaluation/trial3>,
